      "value": "<p>You pour positive energy into ordinary stones, granting them temporary magical properties. You can target 1 non-magical stone or sling bullet for every action you use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.aBQ8ajvEBByv45yz]{Casting this Spell}. The stones must be unattended or carried by you or a willing ally. The stones become <em>+1 striking disrupting @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.MKSeXwUm56c15MZa]{Sling Bullets}</em>. Each stone can be used only once, after which it crumbles to dust.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spell-effects.Item.YzZs7r8VUOp7PiAW]{Spell Effect: Magic Stone}</p>"
